# Input

```yml
{ first: Sammy, last: Sosa }:
# Statistics:
  hr:  # Home runs
     65
  avg: # Average
   0.278

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,6 +1,4 @@
 { first: Sammy, last: Sosa }:
   # Statistics:
-  hr: # Home runs
-    65
-  avg: # Average
-    0.278
+  hr: 65 # Home runs
+  avg: 0.278 # Average
```

# Output

```yml
{ first: Sammy, last: Sosa }:
  # Statistics:
  hr: 65 # Home runs
  avg: 0.278 # Average
```
